Summary: Configuration header for plane tracking, used to create a spatial context with plane tracking capabilities when passed to OpenXRSpatialEntityExtension.create_spatial_context().  

Description  
Configuration header for plane tracking. Pass this to OpenXRSpatialEntityExtension.create_spatial_context() to create a spatial context with plane tracking capabilities.
